<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0071e3 0%, #0051ba 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        background: white;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 15px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .highlight {
        background: #e3f2fd;
        border-left: 4px solid #0071e3;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        background: #0071e3;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f5f5f5;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Application Received</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{fullName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for applying to become a worker on Fix It Now!</p>
        <div class="highlight">
          <strong>Your application has been received and is under review.</strong>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">We'll notify you via email once our team
            makes a decision. This typically takes 2-3 business days.</p>
        </div>
        <p>In the meantime, you can log in to your account to complete your
          profile and set up your preferences.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{appUrl}}/login" class="button">View Your Application Status</a>
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for your patience!</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>The Fix It Now Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Fix It Now. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>